# 012 — Charts & visualization (Part H)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022).
- Slice 001 (`.slices/001.slice-md`) — created `OpticalConstructor.Ui` and the buildable FuncUI interpretation this slice relies on.
